These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: adventure, action, animation, epic, time-travel, thriller, horror
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: july, august, may, october, june, march, december
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cricket, golf, skateboarding, surfing, swimming
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, subway, train, van
 1. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the person driving the subway is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 6. the person watching action movies is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the van and the person who's birthday is in march##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the person watching animation movies is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is the person watching time-travel movies##1
12. the person watching time-travel movies is the person driving the bike##1
13. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
14. the person who's birthday is in march is the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
16. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
17. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
18. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
19. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Movie-Genre      | action  | thriller        | time-travel | animation      | epic     | adventure      | horror     |
| Birthday   | august | october         | december   | july | march    | june | may |
| Sport         | cricket | skateboarding | baseball | basketball | swimming  | surfing  | golf    |
| Transport     | subway  | train         | bike     | jet-ski    | quad-bike | ship     | van     |

