There 7 different types of food: apricot, artichoke, broccoli, pineapple, pumpkin, raspberry, strawberry
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, alhambra, swisher, baccarat, fonseca, dannemann, old-henry
7 different pets are kept: lizard, horse, dog, goldfish, guinea-pig, ferret, mouse
 1. the person drinking cola is the person eating pineapple##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
 3. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 4. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 7. the person eating raspberry is the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the old-henry-smoker is the owner of the mouse##1
 9. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the baccarat-smoker is between the swisher-smoker and the person eating strawberry##2
11. the alhambra-smoker is the person eating pineapple##1
12. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
13. the fonseca-smoker is between the person eating strawberry and the dannemann-smoker##2
14. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
15. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
16. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
17. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
18. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
19. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
20. the person eating broccoli is between the owner of the ferret and the person eating artichoke##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |     4      |    5    |     6      |     7     |
